PERSONAL AND EDUCATIONAL USE
============================

You are free to:

  • Install and run this skill on your own machines, in your own agent
    environments (OpenCode, Claude Code, Codex, Cursor, OpenClaw, etc.).
  • Modify the skill for your personal workflow.
  • Use the skill to produce designs for your own personal, educational,
    research, or hobby projects.
  • Share modified copies with friends and colleagues for the same kinds
    of personal use, provided this LICENSE and the credits in README.md
    are preserved.

